class:: CytonTest
summary:: for generating synthetic test data coming from a Cyton board (8ch)
categories:: External Control
related:: Classes/OpenBCI, Classes/Cyton, Classes/GanglionSerial

description::
this class acts like a drop-in replacement for link::Classes/CytonSerial:: and link::Classes/CytonWifi::.

note::
does not survive link::Classes/CmdPeriod::.
