examples::

this show how to just rename the board class to get test data instead. no dongle or shield needs to be connected.
code::
(
//var board= CytonSerial("/dev/tty.OpenBCI-DM00DRM0", initAction: {|b| b.start});
var board= CytonTest("/dev/tty.OpenBCI-DM00DRM0", initAction: {|b| b.start});
~board= board;
)

~board.accelAction= {|xyz| xyz.postln};  //start posting synthetic accelerometer data
~board.close;
::
